Title: Implements a land exchange and easements in the vicinity of Cathead Mountain
Summary: Implements a land exchange and easements in the vicinity of Cathead Mountain authorized pursuant to an amendment to the state constitution.
LawCode: Add Art 9 Title 23 §§9-2301 - 9-2319, En Con L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to implementing a land exchange and easements in the vicinity of Cathead Mountain
